Dia sudah menciptakan monster.

695
00:45:08,919 --> 00:45:10,580
Dia persis seperti ayahnya.

696
00:45:10,621 --> 00:45:13,419
Mulai lagi, cerita lama.

697
00:45:13,457 --> 00:45:15,618
Air mata dan air mata.

698
00:45:15,659 --> 00:45:18,093
Oh, Tuhan.
