- Itu ditolak.

1302
01:16:29,365 --> 01:16:32,493
Tn. Dawson, tolong duduk.

1303
01:16:32,534 --> 01:16:34,900
Ditolak.

1304
01:16:34,937 --> 01:16:37,405
Tn. Dawson, duduk!

1305
01:16:37,439 --> 01:16:40,408
Ayahnya Annie jahat.

1306
01:16:40,442 --> 01:16:44,742
Besok hari besar Sam di mimbar...

1307
01:16:44,780 --> 01:16:46,714
dan kita perlu berlatih sedikit...

1308
01:16:46,749 --> 01:16:48,649
agar dia sama
efektifnya sepertimu.

1309
01:16:48,684 --> 01:16:53,178
Aku ingin jadi se-efektif
dirimu, Annie.

1310
01:16:53,222 --> 01:16:56,089
Di mobil Porsche, gagang pintunya...

1311
